// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2306 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 19ed3798-4a56-5ac1-9163-6256a2984594

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*")
